WEBVTT

1
00:41:42.630 --> 00:41:45.030 
容我插嘴 那有正确时刻？
Would any of you fellows have the right time?

2
00:41:45.190 --> 00:41:47.870 
有 我有…十一点过七分
Yes, I have seven minutes past 11.

3
00:41:48.030 --> 00:41:52.470 
- 我的表是刚过十一点  - 我的表停了
- I make it only just after 11.  - My watch has stopped.

4
00:41:52.630 --> 00:41:54.710 
- 我一定是上太紧了  - 所以 就如我所说的…
- I must have overwound it.  - As I was saying...

5
00:41:54.910 --> 00:41:56.950 
抱歉 老兄 我得给老板打电话
Excuse me, old boy. I have to call my boss.

6
00:41:57.150 --> 00:41:58.390 
农业机械…
Agricultural machinery...

